{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1dcb7c77fe","title":"坚决相信和依靠干部的大多数","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5598cd95f1","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"5f6c7e74b5","name":"派性","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","name":"红旗一九六七年第十四期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"c2f4286168","name":"周洪生"}]},"publication_details":{"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"24ffa8e965","type":"paragraph","text":"3","index":0,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"1dd9042767","type":"paragraph","text":"8","index":1,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"9ced0c2cb1","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党是在一个儿万万人的天民族中领","index":2,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"6e5bcf29d9","type":"paragraph","text":"导伟大革命斗争的党，没有多数才德兼备的领导中中中","index":3,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"b57c1d2dbf","type":"paragraph","text":"住安干部，是不能完成其历史任务的。","index":4,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"2812bd5036","type":"paragraph","text":"ANARE","index":5,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"5bb47f5145","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：《中国共产党在民族战学中的地位》","index":6,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"13428d2710","type":"paragraph","text":"王坚决相信和依靠干部的大多数","index":7,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"3924ae926e","type":"paragraph","text":"周洪生","index":8,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"bffda6287d","type":"paragraph","text":"相信和依量干部的大多数，这是我们伟","index":9,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"d6c2ccc01e","type":"paragraph","text":"才结中部的大多数，大使用苹命部是当前革命形势发展的道切需要。","index":10,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"eec9bd76f3","type":"paragraph","text":"大领袖毛主席一货的思想。“二十三条”指没有革命干部参加，就役有革命的“三","index":11,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"53f74514bc","type":"paragraph","text":"出：“我们的绝大多数干部是要走社会主义","index":12,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e9623de1d9","type":"paragraph","text":"道路的”，在一般情况下，好的和比较好的是结合”，就不能很好地货御执行党的方针政策，完成抓革命、促生产的任务。","index":13,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"5da6231019","type":"paragraph","text":"多数：在整个运动中，要逐步做到“依靠于“政治路线确定之后，干部就是决定的","index":14,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"ab9bd27c05","type":"paragraph","text":"楼部大多数”。“十六条”又强调了这个思想。国素。无产阶级文化大革命的经验，每一次","index":15,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e24ad89cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"我们必须按照毛主席的教导，用一分为证明了毛主席的这个科学论断。","index":16,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e6b89b633c","type":"paragraph","text":"的方法，对干部队值作全面的分析，做到心中有谐。我们的干部，大多数是好的和比","index":17,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"2959a650a8","type":"paragraph","text":"有的同志对干部不作阶级分析，而以是较好的，走资本主义道路的当权派只是一小","index":18,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"12e9b8f2c3","type":"paragraph","text":"否支持“我这一派”作为鉴别干部好环和能否振。对大多数于部的功过，要有恰如其分的","index":19,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"ba8e4962f1","type":"paragraph","text":"使用的标准。这是“私”字作径，这是小资产评价。毛主席教导我们：“一个人的工作，究","index":20,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"03b359a958","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的派性作怪。这种把个人和小团体的利竞是三分成绩七分错误，还是七分成绩三","index":21,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"f1524e735e","type":"paragraph","text":"益放在革命利益之上的作法，是完全错误的，分错误，必须有个根本的估计。如果是七分","index":22,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"3c2ed07f7d","type":"paragraph","text":"极不利子团结干部的大多数，并且容易被坏成绩，那末就应该对他的工作基本上加以","index":23,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e6e5402bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"人所利用。肯定。把成绩为主说成错误为主，那就完全","index":24,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"51008dcdad","type":"paragraph","text":"在干部中，确有那么一小摄坏人，是需错了。”虽然中国的赫鲁晓夫长期以来极力推","index":25,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"6f1938c3c1","type":"paragraph","text":"要揭露和打倒的，这就是那些混进革命队值行修正主义的干部路线，但是，总的来看，","index":26,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"dd48853c51","type":"paragraph","text":"的反革命分子和数链，就是死不回头的走资我们党的绝大多数千部、是在毛泽东思想","index":27,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"420c96b8df","type":"paragraph","text":"本主义道路的当权派。不看到这一点，是完的哺育下成长起来的，便们在长期的革命斗","index":28,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"79f1c8dd96","type":"paragraph","text":"全错误的。但是，就整个干部队伍说来，他争中作出了重大的贡献。尽管他们有这样","index":29,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"2ceab4b22d","type":"paragraph","text":"们只是极少数人。那样的缺点或错误，但成绩是主要的，是","index":30,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"da5b03bdb0","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，有一小摄阶级敌人，以极“左”的可以相信，可以依靠的。这个信念，不能","index":31,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e4a44db4fc","type":"paragraph","text":"面目出现，利用革命队伍中有一些无政府动播。","index":32,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"2729703405","type":"paragraph","text":"主义思潮和小资产阶级派性，刮起“怀疑一相信和依靠干部的大多数，包括那些兆","index":33,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"9ac9de1ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"切”、“打倒一切”的妖风。我们必须百倍提过若干这样或那样的错误而背作自我批评、","index":34,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"8c6ad4ce48","type":"paragraph","text":"高警惕，切切不可上当。我们必须彻底打退愿意改正的干部。对干部的错误，要作分析。","index":35,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"513e8f1ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"这股妖风。有些是原则性的，有些是非原则性的。对于","index":36,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"23ce97259c","type":"paragraph","text":"一切无产阶级革命派，要排除各种错误那些犯错误的干部，要“一看、二帮”，要相","index":37,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"10a8cc9b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"思想的抚乱和环人的挑摄离间，坚决相信和信大多数是愿意改正和能够改正的。要允许","index":38,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"405c1f785e","type":"paragraph","text":"依靠干部的大多数，大胆使用革命干部，做人家革命。对干部，主要看他的现在和将来。","index":39,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"f1d469276c","type":"paragraph","text":"执行毛主席干部政策的模范。只要不是走资本主义道路的当权派，而是一","index":40,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"e20c44d6a6","type":"paragraph","text":"一切愿意革命的干部，要打消顾虑，到时犯了错误，并且认识了，改正了，就好了，","index":41,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"4b02888303","type":"paragraph","text":"群众中去，在群众斗争的风雨中活学活用就要大胆使用。犯了错误而愿意改正错误的","index":42,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"ab11c9358b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作，向革命小将学习，接受群众的领导干部，能站出来的都要站出来，都要站","index":43,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"530979b924","type":"paragraph","text":"批评和帮助，认真改正错误，改造世界观，出来工作。","index":44,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"},{"id":"9401099d5d","type":"paragraph","text":"勇于挑重担，为人民立新功。","index":45,"publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe"}],"page":{"id":"c97b4932c6","publicationId":"b4755886-bcbc-4a36-abfc-c35d2370ae8a","articleId":"1dcb7c77fe","start":30,"end":31}}}},"__N_SSG":true}